dcterms:description: TACRED contains 41 semantic relations and a special no relation over 106,264 sentences. The subject entities in TACRED are classified into two types: PERSON and ORGANIZATION while the object entities are categorized into 16 fine-grained types, such as LOCATION and TIME.
dcterms:title: TACRED
